sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import { Box, Typography, Card, CardContent } from '@mui/material'; const TasksPage = () => { return ( <Box> <Typography variant="h4" component="h1" gutterBottom fontWeight="bold"> Tasks </Typography> <Card> <CardContent> <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom> Tasks Module </Typography> <Typography variant="body1" color="textSecondary"> Tasks interface will be implemented here. </Typography> </CardContent> </Card> </Box> ); }; export default TasksPage;
